<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">

<head>

    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="author" content="">

    <title>{% block title %}Accueil{% endblock %} - SylvainSaez.fr</title>

    {% block cssblock %}
        <!-- Bootstrap core CSS -->
        <link href="/Public/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

        <!-- Custom fonts for this template -->
        <link href="/Public/fontawesome-free/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
        <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lora:400,700,400italic,700italic' rel='stylesheet'
              type='text/css'>
        <link href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300italic,400italic,600italic,700italic,800italic,400,300,600,700,800'
              rel='stylesheet' type='text/css'>

        <!-- Custom styles for this template -->
        <link href="/Public/css/clean-blog.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Public/css/style.css">
    {% endblock %}

</head>

<body>
{% block navblock %}
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light fixed-top" id="mainNav">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">SylvainSaez.fr</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler navbar-toggler-right" type="button" data-toggle="collapse"
                    data-target="#navbarResponsive" aria-controls="navbarResponsive" aria-expanded="false"
                    aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                Menu
                <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarResponsive">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ml-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/">Accueil</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/blog">Blog</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link disabled" href="">Portfolio</a>
                    </li>

                    {% if user %}
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Deconnexion</a>
                        </li>
                    {% else %}
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Connexion</a>
                        </li>
                    {% endif %}
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
{% endblock %}

{% block header %}
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <header class="masthead" style="background-image: url('/Public/img/bg/index.jpg')">
        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                <div class="col mx-auto">
                    <div class="page-heading">
                        <img src="/Public/img/profil/pp.jpg" alt="une photo de profil noire" class="rounded-circle">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col mx-auto">
                    <div class="page-heading">
                        <h1>Bienvenue</h1>
                        <span class="subheading">Un petit resumé de ce que je sais faire</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container">
        {% if user %}
            <div class="row justify-content-center">
                {{ user.name }} tu es connecté!
                {{ user.email }}
            </div>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 mx-auto">
                <p>Actuellement en reconversion professionnelle, j’ai intégré le parcours developpeur d’applications
                    Php/Synfony auprès de l’organisme de formation Open Classrooms.</p>
                <a href="/Public/cv/CV-Sylvain.pdf" class="btn btn-block btn-outline-dark" download>Télécharger mon
                    CV</a>
                <p>Actuellement a la moitié du parcours, j’ai eu l’occasion de me familiariser avec plusieurs
                    technologies
                    Web : </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>HTML5 et CSS3</li>
                    <li>Wordpress</li>
                    <li>Bootstrap</li>
                    <li>UML</li>
                    <li>PHP (MVC, POO)</li>
                </ul>
                <p>La suite du parcours me permettra de completer ces connaissances en me formant sur Synfony, les API
                    REST,
                    Javascript</p>
                <p>Ce site a pour but de montrer mon avancée grace a un blog et par la suite l’ajout d’un portfolio qui
                    permettra d’accéder a mes différents projets.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr>

    {{ include('contact.html.twig') }}

{% endblock %}

